Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.world.Entity
      • space.world.NonStationary
        • space.world.Container
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ViewableNonStationary, ViewableObject, ViewableOpenable, Lockable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chest, Wallet

    public abstract class Container
extends NonStationary
implements ViewableOpenable, Lockable
    Represents a container which allows other entities to be placed inside it or take entities out of it. Can be opened or closed and locked or unlocked.
    Author:
    Maria Libunao
